"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"這個願望，星星根本不可能幫我實現。\n能夠實現的，只有我自己……我早有這樣的自覺。\n所以，我製造了比以前更多與你相處的機會","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"因為我認為只要這麼做，就能實現短籤上的願望。\n……然而，只有聽你的演奏一事，我仍然繼續逃避","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"那時，久違地聽到你的演奏……\n我感到你的音色不會被技術侷限，\n非常有魅力","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"『盡情享受音樂』……你演奏出這種我所沒有的音色。\n為了不輸給你，我想獲得不會被任何事物左右的評價，\n一直磨練技術至今","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"但我清楚地察覺到，我的音色什麼的……\n不過只是這種程度的『無聊的音色』","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"不想輸給你……\n僅只是為此而彈奏的吉他的音色，\n無聊是理所當然的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"我已經……我已經受夠了。\n不管是持續彈奏著『無聊的音色』的自己，\n還是與短籤上的願望漸行漸遠的自己，全部……全部！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"charac